62
00:02:13,640 --> 00:02:15,880
Fight to the last breath

63
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:21,960
Fight to the last breath

64
00:02:26,600 --> 00:02:27,840
Chentang Pass

65
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:29,240
Will never fall

